  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How can I become a Flipkart distributor?",
  "response": "To become a Flipkart distributor, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Register on Flipkart Seller Hub**: Visit the Flipkart Seller Hub website and sign up for a seller account. Provide the necessary details such as your name, email address, and phone number.\n\n2. **Choose Your Business Model**: Flipkart offers two business models - Flipkart Advantage and Flipkart Marketplace. Under Flipkart Advantage, Flipkart handles warehousing, packaging, and shipping. In Flipkart Marketplace, you handle these responsibilities yourself.\n\n3. **Complete KYC (Know Your Customer) Process**: You will need to submit your personal and business documents such as PAN card, Aadhaar card, bank account details, and address proof to complete the KYC process.\n\n4. **List Your Products**: Once your account is set up and verified, you can start listing your products on the Flipkart platform. Ensure that you provide accurate product details, images, and pricing.\n\n5. **Set Up Your Warehouse**: If you choose the Flipkart Marketplace model, you will need to set up a warehouse or use your existing one to store and manage your inventory. Make sure it meets Flipkart's warehousing standards.\n\n6. **Shipping and Fulfillment**: For Flipkart Marketplace, you will need to handle shipping and fulfillment. You can either use your own logistics or partner with a third-party courier service that is integrated with Flipkart.\n\n7. **Start Selling**: Once everything is set up, your products will be live on Flipkart, and you can start selling to customers. Monitor your sales, manage your inventory, and ensure timely shipping to maintain good seller ratings.\n\n8. **Customer Service**: Provide excellent customer service to handle any queries or issues that customers may have. Good customer service can lead to positive reviews and increased sales.\n\n9. **Scale Your Business**: As you gain experience and your business grows, you can expand your product range, increase your inventory, and explore new opportunities within the Flipkart ecosystem.\n\nBy following these steps and maintaining a high level of service, you can become a successful Flipkart distributor.",
